Nicky Genesis is taking you on a 2 hour sonic and visual journey with her sundown set at Lake Tahoe, Nevada. Experiencing the beautiful nature, witnessing the sky change colors and transform as the sun descends. The water and trees displayed such vibrant colors, and every section different from one another. Through this live sunset DJ set, you’ll hear a collection of tech house, latin tech house, latin house, progressive house and deep house. Playing alongside the beautiful water landscape was such a fulfilling experience. I am so grateful for my team for helping make this all happen. I love creating these experiences and hope you enjoy this musical journey!
Nicky Genesis Live @ Lake Tahoe - Sundown Set 2023

Keith Mac's Special Sauce (Vol.1)' is the first installment of my brand new monthly mix series launching on YouTube and Soundcloud. The idea behind these mixes is to deliver a curated musical experience more suitable for repeated listening when compared to the more relaxed 'Keith Mac's House Party' weekly streams where I spend quite a lot of time bantering on the mic with folks in the chat. Without those distractions, expect upfront selections and some added effort on my end on the "musical journey" aspect of what makes a fun mix worth listening to. LMK how I did in the comments!

We’re proud to welcome Takt for our first release of the year, including a soulful remix from croatian talent ANNĒ.

Coming from Oslo, Norway, musical expression has been a journey of development for Takt. From groovy and playful to up-tempo with tribal influences, high quality productions have always been her main focus. Her passion for techno has made her an appreciated DJ. With performances at Melkweg in Amsterdam and Villa in her home town, she has been a central figure in the scene, being part of numerous electronic music concepts and collectives.

On her side, ANNĒ delivers a mesmerizing remix closing this EP in the perfect way.

Experience a 4-tracker EP from two upcoming women making waves in the techno scene.
